--- linux-2.6.9-rc1-mm4-orig/drivers/video/tdfxfb.c	2004-09-08 12:45:38.552927032 +0800
+++ linux-2.6.9-rc1-mm4/drivers/video/tdfxfb.c	2004-09-08 12:47:28.012286680 +0800
